# Bitcoin Converter API Documentation

...

## Security Best Practices

### Input Validation

- Always validate and sanitize user input before making API calls.
- Follow the guidelines for input validation provided in the [API Security](../security.md#input-validation) section.

### Authentication

- Securely manage API keys or authentication tokens.
- Implement proper authentication mechanisms as described in [API Security](../security.md#authentication-and-authorization).

### Encryption

- Ensure data encryption is used for sensitive information.
- Refer to the [API Security](../security.md#data-encryption) section for details on encryption protocols.

### Reporting Security Issues

If you discover a security issue, please report it following the guidelines outlined in the [Security Considerations](../security.md#reporting-security-issues) section.
